snippet: Homicide charges have been dismissed — at least temporarily — against a couple accused of killing the woman's severely disabled daughter by withholding food and medical care....

headline.print_headline: Charges Tossed in Death of Disabled New York Girl
headline.main: Charges Tossed in Death of Disabled New York Girl

lead_paragraph: Homicide charges have been dismissed — at least temporarily — against a couple accused of killing the woman's severely disabled daughter by withholding food and medical care.
